Just call me Shitou.

00:29:45.380 --> 00:29:47.060
This is my business partner,
Wang Zeyuan.

00:29:48.220 --> 00:29:48.540
Hello.

00:29:48.660 --> 00:29:49.100
Pleasure to meet you.

00:29:50.340 --> 00:29:50.860
And this

00:29:51.100 --> 00:29:52.260
is our national pride,

00:29:52.700 --> 00:29:53.780
the Venus of the Parisian scene,

00:29:53.980 --> 00:29:54.860
Ms. Tan Siting.

00:29:56.140 --> 00:29:57.860
Is it because of my foot that you

00:29:58.540 --> 00:29:59.380
describe me that way?

