Ms. Wen,

00:42:44.580 --> 00:42:46.580
at a time like this, your priority
should be your life's big event.

00:42:47.140 --> 00:42:48.740
Don't let the concert distract you.

00:42:48.860 --> 00:42:49.460
Right?

